title: Hip Hop Air Horn
summary: The best Android air horn app.
description: This app adds swag to your social events. Also supports Android Wear with a native app. Just click the watch to play the sound on the phone.For wear devices, this could also be useful to help find your phone on a cluttered desk or in the couch cushions.
descriptionHTML:
This app adds swag to your social events. Also supports Android Wear with a native app. Just click the watch to play the sound on the phone.

For wear devices, this could also be useful to help find your phone on a cluttered desk or in the couch cushions.
comments: Works on my watch again? Love this app!
